objects.name: cigar
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE cigar (id INTEGER NOT NULL, hash VARCHAR (64), product_id INTEGER, size_id INTEGER, purchase_date DATE, purchase_price NUMERIC (12, 2), location_id INTEGER, owner VARCHAR (64), PRIMARY KEY (id), FOREIGN KEY (owner) REFERENCES users (id), UNIQUE (hash), FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES product (id), FOREIGN KEY (size_id) REFERENCES size (id), FOREIGN KEY (location_id) REFERENCES location (id))

objects.name: container
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE container (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	owner VARCHAR(64), 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	type_id INTEGER, 
	parent INTEGER, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(owner) REFERENCES users (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(type_id) REFERENCES container_type (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(parent) REFERENCES container (id)
)

objects.name: product
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE product (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	brand_id INTEGER, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(brand_id) REFERENCES brand (id)
)

objects.name: transfer
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE transfer (id INTEGER NOT NULL, cigar_id VARCHAR (64), from_id INTEGER, to_id INTEGER, date DATETIME, PRIMARY KEY (id), FOREIGN KEY (cigar_id) REFERENCES cigar (id), FOREIGN KEY (from_id) REFERENCES location (id), FOREIGN KEY (to_id) REFERENCES location (id))

objects.name: container_type
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE container_type (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	PRIMARY KEY (id)
)

objects.name: brand
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE brand (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	PRIMARY KEY (id)
)
rows: La Familia de la Casa de Hidalgo

objects.name: container_inventory
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE container_inventory (container_id INTEGER, hash VARCHAR (64), FOREIGN KEY (container_id) REFERENCES container (id), FOREIGN KEY (hash) REFERENCES cigar (hash))

objects.name: rating
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE rating (id INTEGER NOT NULL, owner VARCHAR (64), cigar_id VARCHAR (64), session_id INTEGER, app_notes VARCHAR (200), app_score INTEGER, smoke_notes VARCHAR (200), smoke_score INTEGER, taste_notes VARCHAR (200), taste_score INTEGER, overall_notes VARCHAR (200), overall_score INTEGER, PRIMARY KEY (id), FOREIGN KEY (owner) REFERENCES users (id), FOREIGN KEY (cigar_id) REFERENCES cigar (id), FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES session (id))
rows: Lots of peppery spice and some woodiness.
Somewhat uneven burn. This may have been my own fault due to smoking while changing the oil in the car.  Otherwise it seemed totally fine.

objects.name: size
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE size (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	width_64 NUMERIC(12, 2), 
	width_mm NUMERIC(12, 2), 
	length_cm NUMERIC(12, 2), 
	length_in NUMERIC(12, 2), 
	PRIMARY KEY (id)
)

objects.name: session
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE session (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	owner VARCHAR(64), 
	date DATE, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(owner) REFERENCES users (id)
)

objects.name: session_inventory
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE session_inventory (session_id INTEGER, cigar_id VARCHAR (64), FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES session (id), FOREIGN KEY (cigar_id) REFERENCES cigar (id))

objects.name: location
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE location (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(64), 
	owner VARCHAR(64), 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(owner) REFERENCES users (id)
)
